"title": "4006: creation, origin of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4006",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The free act of God based on his own wisdom and power, forming the whole natural order by his word.</p>\n<h2>God is Creator of the universe and everything in it</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:6\">NEH 9:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:1\">GEN 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:1\">GEN 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:1-Ps24:2\">PSA 24:1–24:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:22-Prov8:31\">PRO 8:22–8:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:11\">ECC 3:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:5\">ECC 11:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:1-Isa66:2\">ISA 66:1–66:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:16\">JER 10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:19\">JER 51:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:3\">JHN 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:24\">ACT 4:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:50\">ACT 7:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:15\">ACT 14:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:24\">ACT 17:24</a></p>\n<h3>Light and darkness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:3-Gen1:5\">GEN 1:3–1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:7\">ISA 45:7</a></p>\n<h3>The heavens</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps136:5\">PSA 136:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:6-Gen1:8\">GEN 1:6–1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:6\">PSA 33:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:5\">PSA 96:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:8\">AMO 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:7\">REV 14:7</a></p>\n<h3>The land</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:9-Gen1:10\">GEN 1:9–1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:5\">PSA 95:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:25\">PSA 102:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:5-Ps104:6\">PSA 104:5–104:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:14\">GEN 1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:11\">EXO 20:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:17\">PSA 74:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:24\">PSA 118:24</a></p>\n<h3>The sea and sea creatures</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:5\">PSA 95:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:20-Gen1:22\">GEN 1:20–1:22</a></p>\n<h3>Birds</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:20-Gen1:22\">GEN 1:20–1:22</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Land animals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:24-Gen1:25\">GEN 1:24–1:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:15\">JOB 40:15</a></p>\n<h3>The human race</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:26-Gen1:27\">GEN 1:26–1:27</a></strong> <em>Genesis witnesses to order and progression in God's creative activity. The creation of Adam and Eve is not merely the end point, but the climax to the sequence.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:7\">GEN 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:21-Gen2:22\">GEN 2:21–2:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:1-Gen5:2\">GEN 5:1–5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:6\">DEU 32:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:3\">PSA 100:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:14\">PSA 139:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:31\">PRO 14:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:5\">PRO 17:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:2\">PRO 22:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:1\">ECC 12:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:7\">ECC 12:7</a></p>\n<h3>The role of Jesus Christ in creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:3\">JHN 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:10\">JHN 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:6\">1CO 8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:16\">COL 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:2\">HEB 1:2</a></p>\n<h3>The role of the Spirit in creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:4\">JOB 33:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:2\">GEN 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:30\">PSA 104:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:12-Isa40:13\">ISA 40:12–40:13</a></p>\n<h2>The creation of the world</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:1\">GEN 1:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:3\">HEB 11:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:9\">PSA 33:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps148:5\">PSA 148:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:17\">ROM 4:17</a></p>\n<h2>The original creation was complete and perfect</h2>\n<h3>Its completion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:1\">GEN 2:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:2-Gen2:3\">GEN 2:2–2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:11\">EXO 20:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:12-Isa48:13\">ISA 48:12–48:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:3\">HEB 4:3</a></p>\n<h3>Its perfection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:31\">GEN 1:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:10\">GEN 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:12\">GEN 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:18\">GEN 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:21\">GEN 1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:25\">GEN 1:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:29\">ECC 7:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:18\">ISA 45:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:4\">1TI 4:4</a></p>\n<h2>The witness of creation</h2>\n<h3>Creation should cause people to worship God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:11\">REV 4:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:6\">NEH 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:1-Ps19:4\">PSA 19:1–19:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:6\">PSA 95:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps148:5\">PSA 148:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps148:13\">PSA 148:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:20\">ROM 1:20</a> <em>God's power and deity is witnessed through the created order.</em></p>\n<h3>Sinners refuse the witness of creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18-Rom1:20\">ROM 1:18–1:20</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Believers receive the witness of creation by faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:3\">HEB 11:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:6\">GEN 6:6</a></p>",
